user.biography:
🎥 YouTuber by day  🎥 
🇺🇸 747 pilot by night ✈️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Hartsfield-Jackson Atlanta International Airport with @tsa, @74gear, and @deahq. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: If I look sweaty and nervous it's because right before this I was selected for random drug traffic screening and I thought they were going to do a cavity search on me old school style... but the thing behind me X-rays your insides to see if you are carrying drugs. 😮‍💨 I wasn't excited about the idea of a full body X-ray, but it sounded a lot better than Hank and a box of blue rubber gloves 😂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Miami International Airport with @eltamdskincare, @airbus, @boseaviation, @garminaviation, @geaviation, @boeing, and @74gear. May be an image of airplane and outdoors.

node.text:
What summer days with your #747 umbrella looks like… 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in St. Louis Lambert International Airport with @74gear. May be an image of 1 person, flower and nature.

node.text:
5 bee stings later... I got a picture for gram… 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Somewhere in the Sky with @cirrusaircraft, @airbus, @boseaviation, @garminaviation, @geaviation, @boeing, and @74gear. May be an image of airplane.

node.text: Had this plane fly up vertically next to me while I was #flying today. I guess #Maverick made it to the #airlines 😂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Wittman Regional Airport with @cirrusaircraft, @embryriddledaytona, @boseaviation, @garminaviation, @oshkosh_aviation, and @74gear. May be an image of 1 person, airplane and indoor.

node.text:
Am I on my way to #Oshkosh ? Nope 👎🏻 Don’t do anything out there I wouldn’t do… but if you do, send me the story for #cockpit confessionals 😆 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Ted Stevens Anchorage International Airport with @cirrusaircraft, @anchoragedailynews, @embry_riddle_prescott, @airbus, @geaviation, @boeing, @embraer, @74gear, and @ancairport. May be an image of airplane.

node.text: Found this cool #planespotter location, not sure why more people don't come out here! 🤷 Close to the #runway and pretty good views of planes closeup and in the distance 😉

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Portland International Airport with @runnersworldmag, @511tactical, @pdxairport, and @74gear. May be an image of 1 person, tree and nature.

node.text:
I didn't plan on going on a hike during my #layover even though I left the hotel with a backpack, water and sunscreen... but here I am with a bright red shirt on so ALL of the mosquitos can find me out here!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Ted Stevens Anchorage International Airport with @lululemon, @alaskaair, @eccoshoes, @anchoragedailynews, @boeing, @74gear, @anchoragepolice, and @ancairport. May be an image of footwear.

node.text:
Sometimes you’re a bad boy and break your #747 so all you can do is stare at #airtrafficcontrol and wonder... Is today the day they are going to tell me to "Punch it!" 🙏 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber on July 13, 2021 tagging @omega, @airbus, @breitling, @boeing, and @74gear. May be an image of 1 person, airplane and indoor.

node.text: Just a boy and his #Boeing #747 waiting for my 400 passengers to show up and sit in these “VERY DANGEROUS” seats 😂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Miami International Airport with @omega, @cirrusaircraft, @iflymia, @airbus, @boseaviation, @garminaviation, @geaviation, @boeing, @74gear, and @breitling_usa. May be an image of airplane and indoor.

node.text:
Rainy night at #MIA #airport and I am back here babysitting everyone instead of flying 😤
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Miami International Airport with @omega, @menshealthmag, @gq, @amtrak, @rayban, @74gear, and @breitling_usa. May be an image of 1 person, wrist watch and outdoors.

node.text: Somewhere it’s written “Don’t play on #train tracks (unless you’re a #pilot ) “ … you’re just going to have to take my word for it 😂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Airline Pilot Kelsey |YouTuber in Ted Stevens Anchorage International Airport with @natgeotravel, @anchoragedailynews, @embry_riddle_prescott, @airbus, @discovery, @boeing, @74gear, and @anchoragepolice. May be an image of airplane and nature.

node.text:
Still don't get why people love #flying so much, I mean the views up here are terrible 😉 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
